{"tid":888634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【誤傳死訊】無綫斥傳聞沒根據 樂易玲︰聽說利孝和夫人在醫院","createTime":"2018-11-04T02:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T04:17:17.000Z","uid":195944,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8d4545ed9439e286db033dab28b02d19068ab29a","tid":888634,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T02:35:33.000Z","msg":"現年93歲的利孝和夫人晚上驚傳死訊，無綫企業傳訊部接受明報記者查詢時強調︰「完全沒有根據的傳聞。」陳志雲說他沒有聽到消息，無綫高層樂易玲就透露︰「聽說她在醫院。」<br />\n<br />\n利孝和夫人女兒利蘊珍兩日前在Instagram分享家庭照，照片中的利孝和夫人化了妝、身穿粉色上衣，雖然看來有點瘦，但精神也不錯，更手執雞翼來吃，似乎吃得非常滋味﹗<br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1541258086441&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20181103\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1541258086441%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20181103&d=PA4%2BDzYEZCZIURZfFi40ENibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=54392358\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1541258086441%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20181103&h=9d615f83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1541258086441&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20181103</a>"},{"pid":"2a7de9c978507b7242a1c73a3988f60d59849668","tid":888634,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T02:55:48.000Z","msg":"無得睇方小姐同利夫人一齊切蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d915ba8ac255ea7d6826a241e70f10ce3362cece","tid":888634,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T03:03:05.000Z","msg":"係真嘅話今年真係死得人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278926e8c7e2d6efa1063597142ca37816b393c8","tid":888634,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d915ba8ac255ea7d6826a241e70f10ce3362cece","tid":888634,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T03:03:05.000Z",